stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Active: store (v1)\nchecksum computed\nSecretStored

  Active --> Active: resolve\nintegrity verified\nSecretResolved
  Active --> Active: rotate (vN+1)\nvalidate (present · changed · not deleted)\nnew checksum · SecretRotated
  Active --> Deprecated: deprecate
  Deprecated --> Active: rotate (vN+1)

  Active --> Deleted: delete\nSecretDeleted
  Deprecated --> Deleted: delete\nSecretDeleted

  Deleted --> [*]

  note right of Active
    resolve is the ONLY value-revealing call.
    store / rotate / list / events / snapshots
    all redact the value.
    Prior versions remain resolvable by version.
  end note

  note right of Deleted
    Removed from the provider;
    resolve → SecretNotFoundError.
    delete is idempotent.
  end note
